# Add this file to your neovim folder and make it read only

Hotkeys:

SPACE - h - k                 : Show hotkeys
SPACE - g - d                 : Go to definition
SPACE - g - r                 : Go to reference
SPACE - t                     : Toggle nerdtree
SPACE - SPACE - b             : Format black (Python)
SPACE - SPACE - p             : Format Prettier
SPACE - SPACE - g             : Format GoFmt
SPACE - SPACE - u             : Toggle UndoTree
SPACE - SPACE - f             : Find Files (FZF & RIPGREP)
SPACE - SPACE - SPACE - g     : Toggle Go MetaLinter
Control - p                   : Git files (git ls-files)
SPACE - SPACE - c             : Comment or Uncomment line
SPACE - Tab                   : Go to next buffer in list
SPACE - Tab - Tab             : Go to prev buffer in list

SPACE - h                     : horizontal split window
SPACE - v                     : vertical split window
Control - h                   : switch to left split window
Control - j                   : switch to down split window
Control - k                   : switch to up split window
Control - l                   : switch to right split window

TAB                           : switch to next window tab
Shift - TAB                   : switch to previous window tab
Shift - t                     : create a new tab
